Class Quiz

java.lang.Object
org.jaspr.hr.demo.Quiz
public class Quiz extends Object
A simple model class representing a quiz with an id, title, description,topic,number of questions, author and array of questions

      Constructs a new Quiz with the specified title, description,topic,number of questions, author.
      Parameters:
      title - the title of the quiz
      description - the description of the quiz (used as a prompt for AI)
      topic - topic of quiz
      numOfQuestions - number of questions in the quiz (also used to prompt AI)
      author - id of the user who made the quiz
